<div id="article_images"><div class="article_images_primary_container"><div class="article_images_primary"><a class="lightbox" rel="lightbox" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130501040840/http://www.thedrum.com/uploads/drum_basic_article/107384/main_images/lisa_with_hairx_0.jpg" title="Appointment: Markwell moves to editor of Independent on Sunday"><img onerror="this.style.display='none'" itemprop="image" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20130501040840im_/http://www.thedrum.com/uploads/styles/home_page_featured/public/drum_basic_article/107384/main_images/lisa_with_hairx_0.jpg?itok=B5RHerT-" width="235" height="167" alt="Appointment: Markwell moves to editor of Independent on Sunday"/></a><span class="img_caption">Appointment: Markwell moves to editor of Independent on Sunday</span></div></div></div><div itemprop="description" class="clearfix" id="body-content">
  <div itemprop="articleBody"><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>The appointment of Lisa Markwell as editor of the Independent on Sunday, a move from her current role as executive editor of The Independent and the i, has been announced by the newspaper's owner via Twitter.</p>
<p>Evgeny Lebedev informed Twitter users of the news on Friday afternoon, noting that Markwell is one of two female editors, alongside the London Evening Standard's Sarah Sands.</p>
<blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p>Very pleased to say the hugely talented @<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130501040840/https://twitter.com/lisamarkwell">lisamarkwell</a> will edit @<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130501040840/https://twitter.com/indyonsunday">indyonsunday</a>. Wish her and her team best of luck</p>
<p>— Evgeny Lebedev (@mrevgenylebedev) <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130501040840/https://twitter.com/mrevgenylebedev/status/327780562410553344">April 26, 2013</a></p></blockquote>
<script async="" src="//web.archive.org/web/20130501040840js_/http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script><blockquote class="twitter-tweet">
<p>That's the second fantastic female Editor in our company - something none of our rivals can match</p>
<p>— Evgeny Lebedev (@mrevgenylebedev) <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130501040840/https://twitter.com/mrevgenylebedev/status/327780770020200448">April 26, 2013</a></p></blockquote>
<script async="" src="//web.archive.org/web/20130501040840js_/http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script><p>
Other titles Markwell has worked for include Condé Naste, Easy Living and the Sunday Times magazine.</p>
</div></div></div></div></div>

<div class="btn-group"></div><ul class="tags"><li class="tag-category"><span class="tag-label">Category</span><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130501040840/http://www.thedrum.com/category/media" itemprop="genre">Media</a></li><li class="tag-location"><span class="tag-label">Location</span><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130501040840/http://www.thedrum.com/location/uk">UK</a></li><li class="tag-tags"><span class="tag-label">Tags</span><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130501040840/http://www.thedrum.com/search/site/The%20Independent%20on%20Sunday" itemprop="keywords">The Independent on Sunday</a><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130501040840/http://www.thedrum.com/search/site/Lisa%20Markwell" itemprop="keywords">Lisa Markwell</a></li></ul><div id="block-dfp-drum-mpu-newsarticle" class="block block-dfp">

    
